            provoked: ["Mallory keeps score."],
            idle: ["I know things I'm not supposed to know.", "The useful information is always adjacent to the useless information.", "I've noticed some patterns. I keep them to myself."],
            hall: ["The catalog entry is accurate. More than most entries anywhere.", "I've read every label in this hall. Some of them are wrong.", "Mallory was placed here. Mallory accepts."],
