            provoked: ["I'll do what you do, but better!"],
            idle: ["I can do what you do.", "Everything you have, I can replicate.", "Mockery is the sincerest form of flattery. I'm VERY sincere."],
            hall: ["I have memorized every exhibit in this hall. I can BE any of them.", "The Mockingbird's plinth is modeled on all other plinths. It's more authentic.", "They gave me a unique position. I mimic the adjacent ones for fun."],
