            provoked: ["You've made an enemy today."],
            idle: ["I have opinions about this situation.", "Things are proceeding as expected. Disappointingly.", "The system works. I've adapted to it."],
            hall: ["Olivia is represented accurately in this catalog. She checked.", "The label captures the essentials. Olivia is satisfied with the essentials.", "This hall has a better organization system than most places I've worked."],
